        <updateDate>2008-07-07T19:28:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Medicare, Medicaid, and MCH Tobacco Cessation Promotion Act of 2004 - Amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to provide for Medicare coverage of: (1) counseling for cessation of tobacco use; and (2) tobacco cessation pharmacotherapy. </p><p>Provides for similar benefits under SSA titles V (Maternal and Child Health Services) and XIX (Medicaid).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
